Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The implications of knowing the distribution of the levels of consciousness in the world are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the purpose of it is the science of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no science of peace, no science of diplomacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And we just invented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What we do is we calibrate the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is international relationships. You can use it in politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In politics, you can say, what is the average consciousness level of the voter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, where must our platform be to appeal to the voter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The people with the biggest mouths are down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The electorate is up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaking your fist with emotion doesn't appeal to these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They think you need a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's applicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's applicable to politics, to business, to advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is your target audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:02:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And what does our advertisement calibrate at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see idiot advertisements out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's this big chunky guy with little blue wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And pregnant women are wandering back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's all kinds of phenomena going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's three initials that keep coming across.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what they stand for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Middle soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this stand for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate is at 135.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seeing millions spent on that stupid ad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So use your advertising budget wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your energies wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your efforts wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your program for a school district.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you have to sell it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the school board here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the parents here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the community here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your program if you want to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,International diplomacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:03:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We already gave examples this morning of why trying to sell democracy in parts of the world is idiotic and stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving every man equally a vote, you got to be out of your mind, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What we consider to be reality in other cultures is called stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sucker and dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And they wouldn't be caught dead telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean they're told the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Told the truth in court?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize he's dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what they do with truth tellers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The boys take you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get, you're at a 180 with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's America at 421.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are the calibrated levels of various countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can see, therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of a program, what kind of languaging,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see what the prevailing sense of reality is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By knowing that, by writing about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of poking in a people's face by publishing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,provocatively,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it is possible to have a science of diplomacy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that might give you some chances of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Chances of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to, before you can sell something,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to know who you're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who you're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That tells you how to phrase it, how to present it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,how to be with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And it also precludes the egotism
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of thinking that our truth is superior to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the abrasive quality of Americanism in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,which has always been an embarrassment to me since World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And to which the French reacted strongly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and they haven't recovered from World War II either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,De Gaulle, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's saving France, yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He was elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He was elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't a freedom fighter in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This tells us who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be our company here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's Walmart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody hates that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Walmart haters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're big, successful, and they're American.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus they make a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That is hateful, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:06:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it or not, bite the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's Walmart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick that where the sun don't shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can calibrate all the companies you invest in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Take out your stock portfolio, and you'll be selling and buying soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all the ones that collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We were working on the book back in, what, 2002 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We did all the major corporations in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a lot of them under 200, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Under 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Which we didn't print or publish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But we didn't have the stock in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But we told people to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of companies that didn't do too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,World Comm and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Appearance is the stock value.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Essence is what the company calibrates at.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all your stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not greed, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you demonize the ego, you get paralyzed with greed and guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you have a responsibility, especially if you're destined to be enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to be the steward of your assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Solar plexus is about winning and fear of losing and greed and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if you succeed, you end up with guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You end up with guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your increase is the price of somebody else's decrease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you have to re-contextualize your assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your assets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Time, how many years you got left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How many hours in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Assets, financial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Personality-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're six foot six and fast on the court,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you have an obligation to respect that capacity, that talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're good at taking shorthand, whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, your talents, your abilities, your assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of greed now, you respect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're grateful for them and you handle them with respect and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe that respect to yourself and to your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't waste years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing around in casinos and things when there's far more important things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I say don't waste time exploring the astral domains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,New age-ism, all kinds of psychics, healers, peddlers, circus clowns on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Play at it if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you blow a few more lifetimes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Except they're more clever at it than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's arrogance that makes you think you can play with the astral domains and not get singed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know of anybody who's played with the astral domain that has not been singed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been at it for eons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The slightest hesitation tells you exactly why you're going to be a buyer of sweetness and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have come from another dimension to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the revelations of Whoopah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The ancient mysteries of Whoopah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you just got glamorized, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's from a different dimension, you're automatically glamorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The child in you is still enamored of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, in a physical universe, you can get a psychic reading that says,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see your grandmother came from Ireland.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, shit, she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How does she know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And your father, who's still in the lodge on the other side, wants you to so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You just got hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hook, line, and sinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all the information about you is public domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got through telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can calibrate the level of truth of anything that's ever existed in time, energy, or anywhere, even a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Being psychic is nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a whole level of consciousness where your psychic is all hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In the mid-500s, as this kundalini energy comes up, you develop the so-called siddhis, S-I-D-D-H-I-S, paranormal capacities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The kundalini energy flows through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You become psychic, clairvoyant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go anywhere out of body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go inside of something, read it, come back out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it in front of witnesses all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in the box?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I went there, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I'm paying the money to learn how to do it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you get mystified and impressed and glamorized by natural domains.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of those entities have been there, I hate to tell you, they were old at the time of Mesopotamia, and Mesopotamia was their high point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget how expert people can be at what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the biggest practice in the United States, practiced 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time a person made the appointment, I already knew what was wrong with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I already got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you on Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've been getting this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already got what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a patient I'm treating, my office, there was a wooden hallway leading into the main clinic and rows of offices and labs and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To get to my office, they had to walk down the row past all the labs and offices and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They walked across the floor to my office, which was somewhat remote.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,By the sound of the footsteps, I can already tell you whether they're better or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can already tell you what I'm going to have to do with the dose of the med.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I already got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I got them on the wrong med.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I better try something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,People are really expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people, by the time you say hello, they already read you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Entities on the other side have been doing that for eons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A little naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to pay your ticket and get your order read.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could do that without getting entranced, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're going to get entranced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already entranced by the magic of it, by the fact that you went there for a reading, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They already got you by curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So the evolution of consciousness goes through evolution, including the spiritual aspect of your own development.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is spiritual begins as naive, childish, the wonderment of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to see this psychic, and she said, your uncle got hit in a motorcycle accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, just wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody know that experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth tellers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's had that experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't been glamorized by a psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You ain't lived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later, and I'm going to read your future, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get what happened and where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the infinite field of consciousness includes everything known about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just thought I'd tell you a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I got five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the rate of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not only the percentage of happiness, but to see what makes a person happy here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,will make you feel guilty up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have a reverse morality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, to not get is a matter of shame and guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, to get creates guilt because you think, oh, that's my solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was wanting gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the vanity of the ego, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Lord, please help me get over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to win the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Level of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And related happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Which we saw on the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That was, skip that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's incongruity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll skip this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Skip this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Skip this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him saying, I should have left the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop the slides here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll resume later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And see, by knowing the basic dictums.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The basic truths.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you don't have to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:16:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to sacrifice the kick out of the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go over Niagara Falls in a barrel for kicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're spiritually aligned, you can't afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What turns you off about doing that is the disrespect for the divinity of his own creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He has so little respect for yourself that you would put yourself in such extreme injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For both death and damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as forcing the commitment of society to come in and save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And then bury you at tax payers cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the sheer disrespect of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For the transitory solar plexus kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, spiritual evolution does require somewhat declining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:17:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And some of the novelties and kicks that come along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be thankful then and respect that your destiny is to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the destiny of 90% of the people here in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rest of the people are going to go back to the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And come back next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see you after lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What time do we resume?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepare people for their inevitable future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We know what everybody's future is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At least 90%.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,10% are going to chicken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Smart chicken out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You've chosen the way to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is going to realign your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The sequencing is not going to be the same as it would have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So you prepare for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We also can talk about what spirituality is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot that is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's labeled as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Peddled as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Merchandised as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know from some of the ways I communicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,spirituality does not mean a feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearts and flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're all going to be happy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll all sing a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll all sing a song like this is the maypole and this is kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you know where the sun don't shine, that's English.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, spirituality does not require being a feat and delicate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and like a wispy little flower singing hymns around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires strength, courage, valor as you get to extremely high levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires the capacity to experience actually physical pain and various agonies
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and to allow nothing to deter you along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is anything but a feat, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes everything you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And without divine help, it's not even possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible to calibrate below 200 and become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have the karma, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We were talking about the level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It emerges around the level that the people call sainthood,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,around the high 500s, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When that kundalini starts to flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't talk about that energy, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But the many of the things that you pick up later in the astral circus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,were actually phenomena that were derived from those states
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel this exquisite sensation running up your spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not having read anything about kundalini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get glamorized by it, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, there's just an exquisite sense of pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that runs up your back, runs up your whole back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and it runs up into your head, like into your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you focus on the left side of the brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it tends to go in that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So this exquisite sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a flowing energy, is all I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's extremely exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you really value that state
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has that quality that goes with it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've never experienced before,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,except maybe in some incredible psychedelic conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,or states of intoxication.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you got a glimpse of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's why they're intoxicating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not intoxicated by the substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're intoxicated by the quality of subjectivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're beautifully still with the right combination of everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the music is perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you are in like an incredible state.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If only it were possible to stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, having once experienced that state prematurely,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.80,0:22:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,now you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You go into anguish and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because when you have to stop the substance,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that state is no longer accessible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, you have experienced that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore, nothing less will ever do in overtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, at least energy 540,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.05,0:22:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,which is supplied by the 12-step groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to feel naturally that which was artificial before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.68,0:23:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That condition keeps coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going from unconditional lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say, that energy begins to flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Around 560, around 570.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the energy is not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a quality of phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And the quality,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the things the energy does is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you become clairaudient, clairvoyant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you can go inside a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We were talking about it at lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's a message in a closed box.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can look at the box, project yourself in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,read it, and come back out and say, it says, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.23,0:23:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And they open the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a thing that says, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.84,0:23:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can go where you've never been
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and know exactly how to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is hold the destination in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:24:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and you automatically see exactly where to park
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of Lincoln Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you get there, the first car on the right-hand side,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the nearest, most wonderful parking place of all time,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of Lincoln Center, is the Lincoln Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you drive up, they pull out and you drive in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.73,0:24:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.48,0:24:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Life just unveils that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why they call it the course of miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.35,0:24:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because that becomes normal, normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.85,0:24:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And not that you have an expectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.25,0:24:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not, there's nobody trying to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.05,0:24:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomena occur of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the side phenomena of the cities is,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.81,0:24:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've described before, it would like flow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.77,0:24:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It would like flow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.31,0:24:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It would like flow out from the heart chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.27,0:24:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would go places and bring about healings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.51,0:24:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and the miraculous and, you know, phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.04,0:24:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that from the Newtonian paradigm would be called miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.95,0:24:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In its own paradigm, it's natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.23,0:25:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But outside of that paradigm, they'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.65,0:25:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,how did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.13,0:25:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you didn't do it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.13,0:25:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.93,0:25:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomena is of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.41,0:25:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a divine energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.58,0:25:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always got that the people to whom it flowed had been praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.21,0:25:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be like you're an antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.52,0:25:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And the car is turned upside down as you turn the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.21,0:25:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And the highway, the wheels are actually still spinning right here on I-17.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.38,0:25:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And you feel the energy shoot out and shoot into the people within the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.30,0:25:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then all of a sudden, the energy stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.67,0:25:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And you got the people in the car were praying, dear God, please help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.19,0:25:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That energy just shoots directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.76,0:25:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're like the nearest sending radio antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.91,0:25:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the program goes to them, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.50,0:26:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not any personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.00,0:26:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That fact is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.31,0:26:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It performs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.35,0:26:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I could keep you the rest of the afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.77,0:26:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and tell you how the phenomena it would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.64,0:26:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It fixed 100-watt hi-fi amplifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.03,0:26:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy was going there, and the amplifier was blown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.40,0:26:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And somebody said, there's something wrong with the amplifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.09,0:26:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.68,0:26:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, the amplifier go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.98,0:26:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy said, I saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.85,0:26:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what actually happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.11,0:26:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Radio repair, he said, I saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.27,0:26:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, that was a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.03,0:26:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, somehow the subject of the course of miracles comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.43,0:26:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, oh, it's just what the world calls the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.84,0:26:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, he says, I'm really interested in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.21,0:26:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I had one copy, extra copy left of the course of miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, well, here, here, this is what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.71,0:26:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said, oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.42,0:26:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how just one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.53,0:26:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the only reason he came there
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.61,0:27:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was to make contact with the course of miracles and get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.42,0:27:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the phenomena just was a phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.42,0:27:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Those phenomena happen of their own, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.55,0:27:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The trick is, don't be glamorized by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.61,0:27:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try and sell them and realize that they are not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.98,0:27:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So somebody we were talking earlier about,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.81,0:27:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,some entities on the other side, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.51,0:27:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the mistake they made because they didn't have a teacher that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.44,0:27:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,forewarned them in advance not to get glamorized or personalized
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.27,0:27:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the cities when they arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.18,0:27:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They lack that education.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.66,0:27:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, they're innocent by virtue of not
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.98,0:27:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,having known the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.03,0:27:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But when they come on, you realize it's equality,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.44,0:27:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.31,0:27:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.31,0:27:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,own them as a personal power, then you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.86,0:27:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,freeze it there and now you become a
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.69,0:27:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,psychic, you know, eons after eons, you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.30,0:28:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,know, you're giving readings in the year
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.91,0:28:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,892 and you're still giving them, because
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.00,0:28:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you're stuck in the glamorization and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.75,0:28:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of that, you know, seeing the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.21,0:28:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,definition of yourself is a psychic
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.80,0:28:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,clairvoyant and all that. So everybody in
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.48,0:28:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the high 500 has become psychic
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.16,0:28:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,clairvoyant, I mean there's nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.48,0:28:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody's telepathic and in that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.81,0:28:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,state you always know what question the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.85,0:28:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,person has in their mind, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.72,0:28:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly what they're thinking, I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.48,0:28:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just natural to the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.00,0:28:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody's telepathic. You can
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.94,0:28:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,experience that even way before the high
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.25,0:28:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,fives, 500s, so-called silent retreats, or
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.59,0:28:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you go away for a weekend somebody's
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.07,0:28:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,house with half a dozen people and you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.50,0:28:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,don't speak from, you know, Friday till
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.33,0:28:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday morning or something, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.46,0:28:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes telepathic, I mean it's
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.70,0:28:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.90,0:28:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody very quickly too, within 24
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.77,0:28:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,hours, you know, you think salt and at the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.81,0:28:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,tenor table and then just as you think
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.27,0:28:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it, somebody hands you the salt shaker, I
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.22,0:29:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,mean it's normal. So it's not a unique,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.31,0:29:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it's when you get out of the linear, the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.16,0:29:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,nonlinear takes over. So a lot of things
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.01,0:29:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,are known by the field and it's not the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.35,0:29:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,person, it's the field, and so that was the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.75,0:29:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.85,0:29:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,About getting glamorized by all that, you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.44,0:29:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,see, the other thing about truth is it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.24,0:29:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't need to be glamorized. So let's
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.94,0:29:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,do the next, let's do the next slide, you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.51,0:29:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,got another slide? That's how the professor
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.77,0:29:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,knew he was about to lose his
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.46,0:29:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,position, he ran out of slides. So that
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.50,0:29:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,brought up then, by consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.07,0:29:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,calibration plus the knowingness from
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.05,0:29:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,within.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.61,0:30:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an awareness of spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.53,0:30:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,integrity, what is integrous and what is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.40,0:30:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,not integrous, and you can sense it, but
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.03,0:30:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in the beginning, if you don't believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.79,0:30:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you can calibrate it. The calibration
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.31,0:30:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,level of various things then, by
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.99,0:30:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,experience, having been up and down the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.09,0:30:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,scale, then you develop what's called
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.75,0:30:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,discernment, the opening of the third eye
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.47,0:30:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Buddhic body is called discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.19,0:30:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be able to be, you sense the real
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.49,0:30:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,from that which is searching for
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.41,0:30:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,advantage and gain, you know. That which
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.29,0:30:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is the real is all that is and has
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.66,0:30:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing to gain, and then by that you can
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.09,0:30:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,identify it. Nothing to gain, doesn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.72,0:30:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a program going for itself, isn't trying
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.84,0:30:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to promote, isn't trying to proselytize,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.14,0:31:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't trying to glamorize, isn't trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.77,0:31:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,tell you, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.81,0:31:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Seduction, that's called seduction, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.02,0:31:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth, because it's completely satisfied by the fulfillment of its own potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.28,0:31:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,has no gain, doesn't need conversation, doesn't need votes, doesn't need members,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.95,0:31:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't need to proselytize, doesn't need to sign you up,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.83,0:31:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't need to control you or intimidate you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.70,0:31:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or pose hypothetical threats whereby to control you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.24,0:31:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's not interested in your sex life, your personal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.08,0:31:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what you wear, eat, dress, and where you go, what you have for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.70,0:31:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't care whether you're a vegetarian, whether you give up sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.07,0:31:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or sex is your lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.74,0:31:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's got to do something, I mean, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.76,0:31:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's got to repopulate the earth, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.63,0:32:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got nothing better to do anyway at that age, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.94,0:32:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So everybody serves in their own way, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.11,0:32:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You get called out of stud service over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.22,0:32:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The world has to get along without your divine gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.92,0:32:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The responsibility of the teacher, then, is to give certain understandings
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.10,0:32:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that preclude their later being taken advantage of and falling off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.24,0:32:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I always feel sorry for fallen gurus because I see the mistake they made,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.61,0:32:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know why they made it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.27,0:32:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know the teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.40,0:32:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know the teaching that they were missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.79,0:33:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, my obligation is to share with you all that I know about the,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.07,0:33:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, likelihoods along the way because all likelihoods are held in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.59,0:33:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,On one side, there's the temptation that gives it attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.11,0:33:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other side, there's a loss or a pain that is the aversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.75,0:33:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll get to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.74,0:33:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the last slide today, the dualities of attractions and aversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.19,0:33:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Having aligned yourself now with the truth, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.15,0:33:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you become dedicated to it, and the way, now, what is the way to where you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.49,0:33:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You've picked your destiny, and you've committed yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.58,0:33:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and now, how do you know which is the right roadmap?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.23,0:33:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, I've tried to provide a reliable roadmap.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.94,0:33:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done some of them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.77,0:33:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done some of them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.74,0:33:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But some people here are new, and it's all new to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.22,0:33:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is true is true all the time, everywhere, for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.19,0:34:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, every advanced mystic is the same, no matter what century,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.90,0:34:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what part of the world, it's always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.11,0:34:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one absolute reality, and it reveals itself in various dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.53,0:34:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the inner subjective awareness and experience of an enlightened master in,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.53,0:34:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say, 4000 BC in India should be the same as 1936 in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.28,0:34:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no difference at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.94,0:34:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence shines forth, unmistakably has what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.36,0:34:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true at all times, all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.07,0:34:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody that possesses the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.13,0:34:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, there's various claims.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.32,0:34:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.65,0:34:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.50,0:35:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And they shoot each other and blow each other up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.59,0:35:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't blow my truth, I'm going to blow you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.03,0:35:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.73,0:35:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably doing it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.23,0:35:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.53,0:35:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You blow up infidels, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.78,0:35:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep you busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.65,0:35:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's full of infidels.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.98,0:35:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If your trip is blowing up infidels, your life's work is cut out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.26,0:35:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up early, go to bed late.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.96,0:35:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Making bombs and all the fuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.57,0:35:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They work their fingers to the bone making bombs to blow up children with.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.09,0:35:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.21,0:35:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Universality.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.26,0:35:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's always true, not exclusive, all-inclusive, not secretive, and not sectarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.51,0:35:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody owes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.71,0:35:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's got an exclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.19,0:35:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to peddle and sell because the truth is obvious, clear, available to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.21,0:35:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone, anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.05,0:36:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All they need is by integrous dedication, they'll really re-experience it themself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.51,0:36:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.00,0:36:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing secret about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.67,0:36:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mystery about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.88,0:36:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, all those who experience it, they're going to experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.07,0:36:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to experience the truth, proclaim it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.50,0:36:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said, it is the most wondrous of the wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.19,0:36:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone precludes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.19,0:36:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.21,0:36:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, I really got enlightened and too bad about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.01,0:36:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he rejected the Hindu teachings which he thought were incorrect, bowed his inner
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.48,0:36:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,muse and arrived at the ultimate state.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.94,0:36:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He then proclaimed it to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.73,0:36:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.03,0:36:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing that one does is to proclaim its pristine excellence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.48,0:36:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.48,0:36:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, there's nothing to sell about it, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.84,0:37:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is available to all and the doorway to the truth is open to all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.78,0:37:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,With no secrets, there's nothing to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.44,0:37:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no stratification, you know, junior master, middle master, higher master, super
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.28,0:37:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,master.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.50,0:37:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.50,0:37:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.65,0:37:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can jump you from master to super master and it's only 5,000 for the workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.50,0:37:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody want to give me five grand, I'll make you a super master right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.26,0:37:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.26,0:37:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what, better yet, I want to make everybody here a super master and now
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.82,0:37:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you better live up to that title.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.82,0:37:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You are now all going to be masters in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.32,0:37:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.03,0:37:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here already has the energy of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.36,0:37:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.38,0:37:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason you're here is to shine that forth through generations to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.05,0:37:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the purpose of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.53,0:37:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.05,0:38:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's open to all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.53,0:38:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.69,0:38:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is hidden, sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.15,0:38:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no magical formulas or mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.78,0:38:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is there about a mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.57,0:38:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it and you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.15,0:38:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you who's throwing the mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.34,0:38:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindergarteners.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.44,0:38:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a secret, Sylvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.92,0:38:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got one too, Betty.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.07,0:38:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Betty, let's form a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.09,0:38:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret club.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.55,0:38:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll call it the Triple Bunny Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.09,0:38:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They got three members.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.65,0:38:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we'll keep it a secret who's members.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.76,0:38:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a sign like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.57,0:38:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Symbols and signs and secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.78,0:38:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.23,0:38:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.61,0:38:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Swear upon your Oz book that you will not relate to anybody that you're a secret member of this society.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.69,0:38:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wizard of Oz.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.75,0:38:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.19,0:38:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to gain or lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.13,0:39:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the bowl is full, there's nothing more it would want, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.26,0:39:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no difference between yourself and that which is all that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.90,0:39:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, it's a nuisance to have to own something.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.88,0:39:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's really a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.28,0:39:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.36,0:39:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To have to own it and get legal papers and the whole business.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.15,0:39:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nicer to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.17,0:39:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.42,0:39:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When I need a piano, I'll borrow it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.15,0:39:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you got to...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.19,0:39:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to own all the pianos in the world and life gets heavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.00,0:39:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-sectarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.13,0:39:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's not limited geographically or culturally or ethnically.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.73,0:39:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the religions, you know, became ethnic, secularized.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.71,0:39:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They really became...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.21,0:40:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll tell you what the error was and it is very prominent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.23,0:40:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of worshiping God, they worship the religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.05,0:40:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Religionism.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.17,0:40:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It replaces God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.88,0:40:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It releases truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.09,0:40:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're worshiping the priests and the holy places.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.86,0:40:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to walk where Baba walked.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.44,0:40:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, people really, they go all across the planet to walk where Baba walked.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.61,0:40:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing about Baba there anymore at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.65,0:40:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you calibrate the holy lands, you'll find they're about 182 or 210 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.55,0:40:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing holy about the holy lands at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.65,0:40:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,People have been blasting each other to death on the holy lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.40,0:40:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to walk over the dry blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.86,0:40:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.13,0:40:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,what isn't a space or locality or personage is nothing that's owned.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.73,0:40:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing, no ritual you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.51,0:40:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.84,0:41:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a member of our class, you got to say regimentary backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.13,0:41:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's why you have such a small class.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.78,0:41:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.17,0:41:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's no code words.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.07,0:41:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no secrets, non-sectarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.01,0:41:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't depend on opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.69,0:41:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is non-linear, not subject to opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.34,0:41:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not subject to opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.61,0:41:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the downside of religion then is actually, if you look at it, you'll see the politicalization of religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.32,0:41:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the non-integrist ego uses religion for its own non-integrist purposes,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.01,0:41:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to control other people, to gain property, to get money out of the peasants,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.34,0:41:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to control the serfs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.69,0:42:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the serfdoms, the fiefdoms, to hand out the titles, it seeks worldly, secular power.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.61,0:42:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It glamorizes itself and it aggrandizes itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.46,0:42:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives itself incredible titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.05,0:42:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Emperor of all of creation, I am the emperor of Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.15,0:42:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when Napoleon went from 460 down to 160 or whatever he was,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.44,0:42:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,for the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.90,0:42:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when Napoleon went from 460 down to 160 or whatever he was, for the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.40,0:42:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when Napoleon went from 460 down to 160 or whatever he was, for the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.51,0:42:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Napoleon was incredibly integrist, contributed a great deal to Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.11,0:42:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when he crowned himself emperor, he defied the sovereignty of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.98,0:42:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because the ruler came via divinity, and divinity in those days was known via the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.92,0:42:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was the pope that declared you emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.38,0:43:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When Napoleon declared himself emperor, and crowned himself, his consciousness calibration went from 460 to 160.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.03,0:43:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,450 or 60, down to 160, and therefore at the Battle of Waterloo. At Waterloo,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.90,0:43:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Napoleon was counting on the power he once had. You know, he was a magical,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.71,0:43:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,mystical midget, right? I mean, when Napoleon stood in front of his troops,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.73,0:43:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,his troops adored him. They adored him. He was a wondrous and marvelous human being,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.80,0:43:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, and I loved Napoleon before he crowned himself. He was a
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.71,0:43:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,great figure, you know, but in that sodoing, he usurped the power of God as
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.80,0:43:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,represented in the culture of its time and he found really the sovereignty of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.90,0:43:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,God. So, and then at Waterloo, of course, he was mincemeat. Okay. No requirements or
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.42,0:44:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,demands. You don't have to promise anything. No membership.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.92,0:44:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sign anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.30,0:44:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to take any secret oaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.86,0:44:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no regulations, no rules or conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.73,0:44:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody gets expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.75,0:44:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Prison can screw up really awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.32,0:44:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.86,0:44:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Say you're sorry that you killed those eight people.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.13,0:44:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.73,0:44:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.86,0:44:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.17,0:44:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A decent regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.40,0:44:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A decent regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.65,0:44:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What stands traditionally is all that's really necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.65,0:44:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to grovel, because that's another ego game.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.32,0:44:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you've groveled your way through, I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.92,0:44:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,how many pairs of knee pads in front of the cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.92,0:44:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what a grand display.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.26,0:44:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you flagellate yourself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.61,0:44:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's all the drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.40,0:44:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all ego drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.69,0:44:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-binding.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.59,0:44:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sign any oaths, contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.03,0:44:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.92,0:45:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's free to come and go as they wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.34,0:45:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, commonality.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.07,0:45:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.98,0:45:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,People have a function to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.71,0:45:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Function to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.84,0:45:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to give the lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.94,0:45:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if I don't give the lectures, who's going to give them?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.84,0:45:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.21,0:45:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.42,0:45:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you are what you do, what purpose you serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.69,0:45:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.69,0:45:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But nobody's like ooh la la by virtue of a title.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.15,0:45:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're the sixth patriarch of the eighth descendant
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.36,0:45:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of the third incarnation of Baba Bum Bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.40,0:45:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.57,0:45:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, the truth is non-linear, so you can't transmit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.30,0:45:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no linear, linearity by which to transmit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.50,0:45:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't get transmitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.51,0:45:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You bump into the Buddha, you were ready for the enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.11,0:45:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you got the enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.57,0:45:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't transmitted from him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.50,0:46:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You walked into the field by karmic design.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.94,0:46:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't like a this Buddha gives enlightenment to a that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.44,0:46:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Devate.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.92,0:46:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.38,0:46:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.61,0:46:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference is there's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.28,0:46:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.36,0:46:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.48,0:46:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.53,0:46:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Devate's vibration and frequency rises to a certain level and welcomes that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.17,0:46:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then in the presence of the teacher, becomes energized by that aura, that vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.32,0:46:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know when you'll need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.36,0:46:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be ten lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.53,0:46:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it could be tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.44,0:46:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as your car turns over, as it goes off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.46,0:46:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And the third flip, you got it, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.63,0:46:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch the car roll along in the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.78,0:46:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.80,0:46:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Big deal, big deal, big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.13,0:46:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.50,0:46:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Commonality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.98,0:46:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspirational.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.21,0:47:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's partly the job of a teacher to try to present information in such a way that it is cognizant of that which is listening to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.34,0:47:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one thing to say it well and good for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.44,0:47:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one thing to be integrous and to state the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.59,0:47:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't ignore the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.09,0:47:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.88,0:47:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say things.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.88,0:47:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I say things that are not considered spiritual, yeah, amongst your feet, you know, where the sun don't shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.01,0:47:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That ain't fancy language.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.55,0:47:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's one reason we have a lot of men in our groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.19,0:47:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of, well, a lot of motivational speakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.61,0:47:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the, you know, you see the video, you taste them on TV, and they're like 90% women.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.92,0:47:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the guys are sitting there like they've just been dragged to the opera, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.76,0:47:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at the next one, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.11,0:47:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the guy sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.28,0:48:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of look attentive to please her, and he's being polite to the speaker, and it's vaguely interesting, but it's not really his, his thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.94,0:48:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't his shtick, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.15,0:48:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I also speak to men, because there's also men out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.00,0:48:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't live in the world of daisies and flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.34,0:48:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're living the world of make a mistake, and you're no longer president of this corporation, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.26,0:48:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.98,0:48:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.98,0:48:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Free to come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.98,0:48:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Commonality.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.98,0:48:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Recognition is the consequence of what you do and what you become.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.98,0:48:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We inspire each other by the example of who we have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.34,0:48:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not materialistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.34,0:48:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to build great edifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.84,0:48:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that there's anything wrong with that, because human nature wants to put in the linear
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.11,0:48:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,world representational.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.46,0:49:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is representational.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.32,0:49:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.32,0:49:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.32,0:49:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Worship.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.46,0:49:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So the great cathedrals are awesome, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.96,0:49:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,National Cathedral in Washington, D.C. is an exact Gothic you'd think you were in the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.96,0:49:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,14th century in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.21,0:49:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible, because that design has come to mean devotion, dedication, worship, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.61,0:49:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Christian ideal of, the essence of Christianity.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.55,0:49:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To worship, so it is a symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.32,0:49:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.51,0:49:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In and of itself, then, it represents an expression, an art form.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.51,0:49:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Architecture is an art form.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.59,0:49:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-temporality.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.38,0:49:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Equality.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.38,0:49:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Equality means this understanding that all of life is equally of value.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.38,0:49:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So during lunchtime we went out in the back, and here was a stunning, I guess what the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.38,0:50:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,world would call a weed or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.42,0:50:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And both of us looked at it, and its perfection was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.11,0:50:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And little berries in the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.11,0:50:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the perfection, the presence of divinity as perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.11,0:50:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In all that exists, it's not exclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.11,0:50:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual truth is not provable.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.23,0:50:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Proof belongs to the world of cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.05,0:50:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Newtonian paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.05,0:50:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be demonstrated, it can be verified, but you cannot prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.51,0:50:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can become it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.76,0:50:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can calibrate the likelihood of its presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.94,0:50:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That still doesn't prove, prove.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.03,0:50:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So proof is a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.03,0:50:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond 500, you can't really prove anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.84,0:50:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only become it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.84,0:50:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't prove love.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.84,0:50:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't prove love.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.96,0:51:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You become loving, and it's your experience, your reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.67,0:51:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.67,0:51:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So 500 and up is not provable.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.67,0:51:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.73,0:51:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystical.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.05,0:51:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What does mystical work mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.05,0:51:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It means it did not come about as a consequence of the Newtonian cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.17,0:51:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Improbable.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.17,0:51:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.17,0:51:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Statistical likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.69,0:51:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystical is sort of a kicked about word.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.42,0:51:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In its true meaning, it means to realize from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.67,0:51:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is mysterious to the intellect, but not to the mystic.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.67,0:51:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.67,0:51:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's mystical, mysterious to the mystic is how people could still fall for the sequential
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.84,0:51:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,linearity of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.84,0:51:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.84,0:51:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mystic then has a tradition in Christianity.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.40,0:52:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There are the great mystics that are revered.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.76,0:52:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mysticism, if you look it up in the Dictionary, the Encyclopedia, a lot of the phenomena that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.59,0:52:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I experienced and I describe in various books is the very same.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.59,0:52:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The various ailments that come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.59,0:52:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And the higher you get, the more they can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.59,0:52:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Like all your nerves are on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.82,0:52:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I warn people of that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.82,0:52:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you decide to drive the whole way, the nervous system is not used to handling energies
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.88,0:52:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of that dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.61,0:52:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget these are logarithmic progressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.61,0:52:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Logarithmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.61,0:52:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So the difference between 785 and 790.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.96,0:52:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.96,0:52:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,785 and 790 is considerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.05,0:52:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And at about 850, it becomes quite a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.05,0:52:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Which we wrote about in this new book, how to handle those levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.11,0:53:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everybody here is going to be enlightened, I'm telling you about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.28,0:53:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it when you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.82,0:53:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a sensation like you're burning from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.13,0:53:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how to transcend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.13,0:53:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.13,0:53:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,from what level on you're pulling up from the collective
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.32,0:53:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,unconscious of mankind. It's not your personal
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.28,0:53:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,karma anymore. It's not your stuff. You already
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.17,0:53:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,cleared that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.00,0:53:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You start pulling from the collective
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.88,0:53:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,over 700, over
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.05,0:53:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,750,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.38,0:53:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,800.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.38,0:53:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You start pulling from the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.80,0:53:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,collective from over 650,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.53,0:53:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,660.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.73,0:53:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.26,0:53:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.96,0:53:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so you see you've already
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.44,0:53:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,cleared all this stuff in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.46,0:53:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,itself. So it's a
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.40,0:53:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,mystification. Why am I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.13,0:53:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing this pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.09,0:53:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Any kind of a spiritual error brings up pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.94,0:53:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're holding
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.96,0:54:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,something somewhere in your consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.03,0:54:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that is not aligned with the absolute truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.13,0:54:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it brings up pain. That forces
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.32,0:54:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you to go within and ask God,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.53,0:54:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Almighty God, creator of the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.15,0:54:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and all things visible and invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.82,0:54:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the son of the Lord Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.75,0:54:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray that you will
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.23,0:54:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,bring forth into my awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.34,0:54:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.00,0:54:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is not aligned with truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.05,0:54:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Something will come out
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.36,0:54:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of some archetype deeply buried
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.17,0:54:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in the collective unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.34,0:54:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And in my own experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.65,0:54:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.17,0:54:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual night was the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.17,0:54:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,toughest.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.55,0:54:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual night kept coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.71,0:54:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be burning all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.78,0:54:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd forgiven everything
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.94,0:54:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,decades ago. What am I indignant
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.26,0:54:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,about? All of a sudden, like a
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.53,0:54:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,rage, an indignation
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.28,0:54:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,at the violation of the truth of God
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.63,0:54:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,came up over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.50,0:54:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it practically fried my nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.30,0:54:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,system to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.90,0:54:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Indignation
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.55,0:54:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,at the desecration
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.34,0:55:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.40,0:55:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and the glee at doing
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.73,0:55:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so, that was bad
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.90,0:55:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,enough. But then the agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.76,0:55:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of large percentage of the population
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.78,0:55:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,with it was what brought up the outrage.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.78,0:55:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Had a heck of a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.53,0:55:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a personal me, which has long
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.92,0:55:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,since given it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.34,0:55:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But beyond a certain level,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.80,0:55:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you're like bringing it up
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.67,0:55:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for the collective consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.63,0:55:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of mankind, as described by Carl Jung.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.15,0:55:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As you see, the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.23,0:55:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated level of consciousness of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.19,0:55:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,has slowly been rising. Not slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.71,0:55:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,been rising rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.40,0:55:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because each being of advanced
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.40,0:55:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness now begins to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.28,0:55:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,take responsibility for some
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.42,0:55:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,portion of the collective.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.17,0:55:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember it being volitional. I'll have to look
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.09,0:55:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,into that. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.05,0:55:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.57,0:55:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.88,0:55:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,odd illnesses and strange
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.30,0:55:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,passing phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.25,0:55:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you suddenly get red and hot and
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.21,0:56:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,sweat and your nervous system goes to
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.25,0:56:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the blink. So with prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.57,0:56:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,then, you sort of become aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.82,0:56:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not within the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.17,0:56:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,intellectual domain. You wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.11,0:56:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in the morning and you suddenly see
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.98,0:56:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is. You see what it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.15,0:56:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is. You see what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.26,0:56:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That if I was really a warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.82,0:56:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of truth, I would be
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.01,0:56:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,defending their right
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.69,0:56:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to forgiveness instead
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.09,0:56:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of making them wrong. You see a
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.03,0:56:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,different kind of an understanding will come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.84,0:56:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden, the energy disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.96,0:56:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you may be okay for days, weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.09,0:56:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,hours, and it may start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.98,0:56:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm just telling you. And the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.96,0:56:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha wrote about it. As I said, when it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.96,0:56:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,became severe, we were in Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.46,0:56:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And Susan pulled out of the side
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.09,0:56:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,table, opened it to
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.03,0:56:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the Buddha. And the Buddha said his bones
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.94,0:56:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,felt like his bones were
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.90,0:56:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,cracked. And I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.11,0:56:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,whoa, yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.57,0:56:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.96,0:56:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So now
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.19,0:57:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what holds people at the various
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.07,0:57:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness levels is
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.94,0:57:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,usually a duality. There
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.13,0:57:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is an attraction and an aversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.11,0:57:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.46,0:57:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the pathway to enlightenment is constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.21,0:57:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,one of surrendering
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.92,0:57:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,both attractions and aversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.17,0:57:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The attraction is to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.71,0:57:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,off. Every ego position
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.59,0:57:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,has a payoff. The
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.30,0:57:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,payoff of feeling right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.36,0:57:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The indignity of my
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.78,0:57:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual night.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.88,0:57:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The desecration of what they've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.15,0:57:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They've grown
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.25,0:57:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,up the great Buddha of
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.67,0:57:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Afghanistan. I mean, one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.88,0:57:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,after another, these people were like
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.48,0:57:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,pushing you to see how far they could
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.98,0:57:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,push you. So
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.48,0:57:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.86,0:57:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,give up that indignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.51,0:57:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The pleasure of that indignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.36,0:57:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And the seduction
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.69,0:57:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of it. You see the seduction of being
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.78,0:57:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,right. And
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.73,0:57:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender to
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.05,0:58:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,humility. With
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.03,0:58:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,humility and the surrender then,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.38,0:58:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there comes a realization
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.94,0:58:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.26,0:58:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And that realization
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.42,0:58:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is of a different dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.03,0:58:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's beyond the duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.78,0:58:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.73,0:58:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.96,0:58:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you evolve then, you're lifting others.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.94,0:58:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.65,0:58:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,lifts the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.51,0:58:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So what can people do to help
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.34,0:58:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the people that are downtrodden in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.44,0:58:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and all? Aside from
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.32,0:58:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the physical support
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.71,0:58:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and very obvious things
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.42,0:58:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you can do, is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.67,0:58:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,by our combined intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.23,0:58:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,by that which we have become,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.51,0:58:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we lift the level of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.84,0:58:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We all lift the level
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.94,0:58:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of the sea. And as the level
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.84,0:58:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of the sea rises, it lifts
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.92,0:58:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,up all the ships on the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.67,0:58:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.82,0:58:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,level of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.94,0:58:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,went from one,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.19,0:59:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what it was, over the centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.46,0:59:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.13,0:59:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,late 80s, it suddenly jumped
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.90,0:59:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,from, I think, 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.51,0:59:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, 190. It was stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.40,0:59:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stuck at 190 for many centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.15,0:59:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then suddenly in the late 80s
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.84,0:59:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,went, bang, up to 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.88,0:59:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.76,0:59:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,October, I think it was last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.69,0:59:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it suddenly went to 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.94,0:59:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, the sea is rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.42,0:59:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The consequence of the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.98,0:59:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,being rising, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.09,0:59:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it precipitates catastrophe
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.98,0:59:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.90,0:59:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.80,0:59:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At 190, Enron wouldn't have fallen
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.63,0:59:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in a rule of calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.38,0:59:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At 205, it falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.76,0:59:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.28,0:59:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The payola works
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.05,0:59:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,until you're
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.40,0:59:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,at the level of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.88,0:59:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now payola doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.67,0:59:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to the clink.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.11,0:59:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Liddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.03,0:59:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.94,0:59:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So here are the,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.98,1:00:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we put them as the classic dualities.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.92,1:00:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We could,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.51,1:00:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, spend a lecture on any one
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.48,1:00:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of them. We all like
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.71,1:00:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is familiar and secure.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.38,1:00:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And we don't want to really make a change.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.59,1:00:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a resistance to change.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.76,1:00:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's the attraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.84,1:00:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be where I'm familiar.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.11,1:00:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want things to stay the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.48,1:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I really
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.80,1:00:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,don't want to
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.82,1:00:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,change. That applies
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.59,1:00:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to you as a person.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.09,1:00:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.73,1:00:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really want to give up being a pickpocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.67,1:00:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I had
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.42,1:00:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to do that in France in one lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.78,1:00:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up being a pickpocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.28,1:00:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, I was good at it, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.46,1:00:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Clever pickpocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.96,1:00:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And they still play the same
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.44,1:00:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,games that we used to play.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.59,1:00:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is familiar
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.23,1:00:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,way of life, and you've got to change.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.01,1:00:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The attraction is
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.09,1:00:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore clinging to things
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.25,1:01:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fear of the new.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.80,1:01:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.21,1:01:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual work brings up
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.15,1:01:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as much as you don't like
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.71,1:01:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain way of being, nevertheless
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.19,1:01:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's familiar, habitual.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.50,1:01:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a certain comfort in that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.26,1:01:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And one has to then surrender that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.75,1:01:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this way is easy,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.40,1:01:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and this one seems to take effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.17,1:01:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems to take effort
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.26,1:01:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to correct myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.30,1:01:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I make the same
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.48,1:01:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,mistake, put it in the wrong place,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.19,1:01:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to now put the effort forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.67,1:01:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't go on the third shelf,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.34,1:01:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it goes on the second shelf.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.98,1:01:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.30,1:01:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,after a couple of times, you automatically put it
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.30,1:01:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in the right place. In the end, it's rewarding.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.38,1:01:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it increases
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.63,1:01:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,your pride.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.00,1:01:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the attraction of pride is,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.01,1:01:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.88,1:01:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of the thing itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.23,1:01:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So all these so-called negatives,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.48,1:01:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't what they are,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.48,1:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the payoff
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.76,1:02:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,juice. It's the ego's
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.11,1:02:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,payola. You lack
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.38,1:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the sensation and the pleasure of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.21,1:02:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hooked on the pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.11,1:02:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so you'll do
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.98,1:02:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,anything on the left side here
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.51,1:02:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to get that payoff.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.88,1:02:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll win, you'll be right, you'll be successful,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.75,1:02:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,prove that guy wrong, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.86,1:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.19,1:02:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,payoff is always the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.94,1:02:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.71,1:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,pride doesn't like to look
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.25,1:02:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,at the possibility of humility.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.82,1:02:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And it confuses
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.82,1:02:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,humility with humiliation.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.94,1:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It means to the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.69,1:02:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to be less than.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.09,1:02:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not realizing that humility
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.01,1:02:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,allows you to be greater than.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.96,1:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Greater than.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.11,1:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of humility, you are greater than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.84,1:02:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.96,1:02:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So pride is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.36,1:02:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,an illusion. It's a self-puffery.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.42,1:02:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the way the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.21,1:02:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,keeps going.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.40,1:02:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it also can be quite proud of its
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.51,1:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,humility, as we all know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.86,1:03:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.63,1:03:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,aspects of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.59,1:03:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is the substitution by
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.23,1:03:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual pride.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.80,1:03:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's very hard for
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.53,1:03:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a group of intelligent people
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.61,1:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,not to get some degree of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.59,1:03:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,at least on the intellectual level.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.15,1:03:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.46,1:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been there, I heard that speaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.48,1:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Or
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.63,1:03:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.23,1:03:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.98,1:03:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.98,1:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they read that book, they're familiar.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.30,1:03:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, if you know a lot of Sanskrit,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.30,1:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that definitely makes you better than other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.94,1:03:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of Sanskrit.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.71,1:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.48,1:03:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,People like anger
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.17,1:03:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because then it gives them a false sense of strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.23,1:03:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel, when you feel angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.15,1:03:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So the animal with anger puffs up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.05,1:03:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The rooster puffs up, the gorilla puffs up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.32,1:03:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea is to intimidate your enemy
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.38,1:03:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to appear stronger than you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.69,1:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger then, one of the things you get out of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.38,1:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the payoff,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.36,1:04:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is an illusion of strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.51,1:04:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now anger is not strength, as you well know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.57,1:04:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, as an opponent,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.11,1:04:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,as an opponent,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.09,1:04:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a trick is,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.11,1:04:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,he didn't see that,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.30,1:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just got him pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.94,1:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I got him pissed off, I got him skewered.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.76,1:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the coach didn't see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.57,1:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to sneak in, to get him into anger.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.53,1:04:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the coach didn't see that. I tried to sneak in, to get him into anger.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.67,1:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the coach didn't see that. I tried to sneak in, to get him into anger.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.21,1:04:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in anger, I can skewer him in a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.59,1:04:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In anger, you take a position, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.44,1:04:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't take a position, you can't be hit,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.86,1:04:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because you intuitively get how he's coming at you,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.00,1:04:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and you intuitively move aside.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.07,1:04:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The kung fu of survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.30,1:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to know before he strikes,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.65,1:04:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,where the strike was coming from,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.03,1:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have to intuit what it was about you
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.76,1:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that was attracting the strike in that area.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.94,1:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you pick out that you took some kind of a stance, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.34,1:05:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your stance that he read,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.09,1:05:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore he came back in that space which you created, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.03,1:05:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so anger then is a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.98,1:05:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In a combative situation,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.03,1:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,other than decoy deception,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.46,1:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which is always worth the try,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.53,1:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you always try to get him mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.76,1:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You kick him where the coach can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.15,1:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.50,1:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes in with anger.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.90,1:05:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.75,1:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With anger, you skewer yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.07,1:05:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is not a strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.42,1:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A strength is wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.90,1:05:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wisdom, that is strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.13,1:05:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy just stands there and reads you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.21,1:05:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,before the bout starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.30,1:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.69,1:05:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.01,1:05:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I did boxing years back, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.92,1:06:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the guy's reading you, look out,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.07,1:06:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,because he isn't coming on with bravado.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.61,1:06:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not coming on with anger.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.96,1:06:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming on with cool calculation.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.53,1:06:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.61,1:06:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So strength then is staying cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.01,1:06:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The attraction here, of course, is to win,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.96,1:06:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,which everybody sees as a gain,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.55,1:06:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fear, of course, is loss.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.32,1:06:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the whole world we live in,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.21,1:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the world of gain and loss.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.53,1:06:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The stock market, everything else is win and lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.34,1:06:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, the other gains are feeling important.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.82,1:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the reasons we like to win is we feel important.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.90,1:06:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives us a temporary sense of empowerment.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.03,1:06:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Empowerment.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.71,1:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a legitimate side to winning as respect,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.26,1:06:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the recognition that the consequence was as a result
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.96,1:07:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own dedication and effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.15,1:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a recognition, which is different than a vanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.07,1:07:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The attraction of money, excitement,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.55,1:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of desire itself, status, these are familiar,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.76,1:07:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm working on them for the next book, because each of these,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.01,1:07:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,are aligned with certain levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.92,1:07:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to stop a few minutes early,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.65,1:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because we don't have time for Nico to chant.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.48,1:07:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we're going to stop at 5 or 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.71,1:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,People love opinions.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.80,1:07:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop any person on the street,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.32,1:07:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and they've got an opinion on everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.88,1:07:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember an old friend of mine that became seriously involved
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.32,1:07:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in a recovery group, spiritual group.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.01,1:07:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And he came over to my house one day, and he says,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.57,1:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, Dave, I've just stunned and knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.07,1:07:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.51,1:07:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, I just realized I don't have
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.34,1:08:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to have an opinion on everything, and I feel so free.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.23,1:08:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not obligated to have one.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.11,1:08:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to fight for one, stand for one, defend one,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.53,1:08:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,create one, position one.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.07,1:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to have an opinion.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.82,1:08:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about the election?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.44,1:08:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.63,1:08:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Democracy in action, how does that sound, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.57,1:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,About catastrophes, well, you know, as Ramana Maharshi says,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.38,1:08:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the world you see, you think you see, doesn't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.96,1:08:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And his recommendation is that you surrender it to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.52,1:08:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,His recommendation is.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.46,1:08:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't know what's right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.53,1:08:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what's the undoing
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.73,1:08:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of bad karma or good karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.22,1:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What looks to you like a catastrophe to other people,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.90,1:08:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it's frankly salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.50,1:08:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who's been on the edge
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.89,1:08:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of catastrophe has been on the edge of catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.06,1:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who's been on the edge of catastrophe has been on the edge
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.15,1:08:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of catastrophe has been on the edge of catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.65,1:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, it was the edge of the catastrophe the guy should let go
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.26,1:08:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and got you the salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.46,1:09:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Without that catastrophe, without your feet being held
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.30,1:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fire, you weren't about to quit, were you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.42,1:09:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's holding people's feet to the fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.92,1:09:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't God cruel?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.02,1:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.13,1:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when I became an atheist,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.28,1:09:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I went from a devout religionist,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.97,1:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as I've told you before, and walking through the woods one day,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.35,1:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,out of nothing, out of nothing,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.38,1:09:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't think about anything,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.46,1:09:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,came to me the revelation of the totality
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.14,1:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of the suffering of mankind throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.59,1:09:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like the opposite of what was later realized.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.26,1:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like it's denial or opposite.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.69,1:09:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw the totality of the agony, the totality of the agony
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.19,1:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of mankind's suffering over eons of time, it was staggering.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.28,1:10:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I went into like shock.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.78,1:10:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly, I became an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.56,1:10:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No God who allowed or created that could I worship,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.72,1:10:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and I became an angry atheist, angry that God could allow.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.55,1:10:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So I held God responsible for what is really the consequence
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.92,1:10:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of the human ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.38,1:10:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking at the consequences
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.27,1:10:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of the collective human ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.72,1:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't looking at the divinity of creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.00,1:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.25,1:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego held God responsible.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.22,1:10:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see how spiritual ignorance, then,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.26,1:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we can fall into the depths.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.22,1:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a serious atheist for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.80,1:10:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To get out of it actually took me to the depths of the lower hells,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.89,1:10:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,not the hells of agony, the hells far beyond agony,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.67,1:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,far beyond, indescribable, which go on for eons.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.93,1:11:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The foreverness of hopelessness,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.57,1:11:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is out of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.42,1:11:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of that, a voice arose, out of somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.92,1:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Some good karma somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.00,1:11:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, old ancestor, for worshiping the bear God
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.97,1:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or something, because out of somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.90,1:11:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a God I ask him to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.01,1:11:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And then came the great, incredible experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.64,1:11:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the going through the valley of death and the death.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.98,1:11:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which you are, literally,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.59,1:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,does die.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.82,1:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience of that which you are does die.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.97,1:11:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And that opens the opposite of that vision,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.78,1:11:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence which wipes out everything,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.09,1:11:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,other than its own reality and truth, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.38,1:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so then, as a consequence of that,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.80,1:12:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,comes the commitment, yes, to share that which you have
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.52,1:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced, witnessed, can verify,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.15,1:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and willing to put your hand on the Bible about.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.42,1:12:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then to combine that with a verification coming about,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.11,1:12:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,through some objective means, such as the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.06,1:12:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,utilizing the scientists, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.51,1:12:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, the personage accomplishes this
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.94,1:12:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world, and having done all that,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.15,1:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have fulfilled my dedication to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.43,1:12:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,as a teacher, this day.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.53,1:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I dedicate it to you, and to your obvious future,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.34,1:12:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you will be doing for others,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.72,1:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because it goes on and on and on and on through eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.92,1:12:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you will become will become
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.39,1:13:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that which triggers that which will become,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.35,1:13:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,which will become, and so you'll see yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.68,1:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,as part of the evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.68,1:13:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's creation and evolution are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.93,1:13:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all right, we're gonna stop, and allow a chanting,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.92,1:13:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a unique experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.22,1:13:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, Niko chants the Lotus Sutra in Sanskrit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.18,1:13:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gives yourselves notice that your chairs
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.97,1:13:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,are just totally accepting of you, as is divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.93,1:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And just lean in the, you know, open,
